Welcome






Bexil   Corporation is a holding company engaged through wholly-owned subsidiaries in investment management and securities trading. Bexil Advisers LLC is a  registered investment adviser and the investment manager to Dividend and Income Fund, a closed end fund (NYSE: DNI) (NAV: XDNIX). Bexil Securities LLC  is a registered broker-dealer trading securities for its own account. 




