Letter from the President 


Welcome to Bexil Corporation!

Our objective is simple, straightforward, and sharply  focused: to increase book  value per share over time. We believe that long term stockholders will  benefit from a rising book value as market recognition builds and investors  come to appreciate Bexil's intrinsic value as well.  Having the value of  your investment in Bexil grow is as important to us as it is to you --  management and affiliates own over 30% of Bexil's shares.

We appreciate and thank you for your interest in Bexil. 





Sincerely, 




Thomas B. Winmill
President 
















PO Box 4, Walpole, NH 03608 Tel: 1-212-785-0900 Fax: 1-917-746-4802
