Company Overview of Bexil Advisers LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bexil Advisers LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity markets. It is based in New York City. Bexil Advisers LLC operates as subsidiary of Bexil Corp.


11 Hanover Square12th FloorNew York, NY 10005United States



Phone: 212-785-0900

Fax: 917-746-4802








